11. Header Mobile Menu Button and Nav (Narrow Screens)
    
    Cellphone size header
        //mytheme >> sass >> theme >> _theme.scss
            #wrapper-navbar
                .top-header-holder {} >>
                
                    @media(max-width: $md) {                   //add padding around phone number box
                        padding-top: 15px;
                        padding-bottom: 15px;                            
                    }
                
                    .container {
                        .logo-holder {
                            display ...
                            img { ... }
                            @media(max-width: $md) {
                                display: none;                          //hides logo when viewport hits cellphone size
                            }
                        }                    
                        
                        .contact-holder {
                            a {
                                @media(max-width:$md) {
                                    padding-top: 0em;
                                    padding-bottom: 0em;                               
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        
                        .navbar-toggler {
                            @media(max-width: $md) {
                                display: none;                            //hides menu icon
                            }
                        }
                        
                        .reservation-btn {
                            @media(max-width: $lg) {
                                font-size:18px;                            
                            }
                            @media(max-width: $md) {
                                display: none;                            //hides reservation-btn
                            }
                        }
                        
                        .social-media-holder, .social-media-holder-tablet {
                            &.social-media-holder-tablet {
                                @media(max-width:$md) {
                                    display: none;                      //hides social media icons
                                }
                            }
                        }                        
                    }

    Redesign the columns and move "contact phone" to the left end of the screen
        //mytheme >> page-templates >> header.php  
